metadata.name: Gratitude
metadata.description:
"Gratitude" is a token of my appreciation to all of my collectors. 
Collectors of the following collections receive 1x Gratitude token via airdrop. 
-Brainleak: Genesis  
-Brainleak: VIAJE Originals  
-Brainleak: VIAJE Editions

Note: Gratitude bridges all of these collections together to deliver special plans to owners of this exclusive token such as; early mint access to *select* artworks, early bidders access, and more.
